Package: nexus-mp-wsl
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: NexusMP - WSL IMAP4rev1 Mail Server
 A high-performance IMAP4rev1 mail server for Windows Subsystem for Linux.
 Supports IDLE, compression, STARTTLS, and advanced mail management.

Package: nexus-mta-wsl
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: NexusMTA - WSL Mail Transfer Agent
 A lightweight Mail Transfer Agent for Windows Subsystem for Linux.
 Handles SMTP queue processing and mail routing.

Package: nexus-smtp-wsl
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: NexusSMTP - WSL SMTP Server
 A robust SMTP server for Windows Subsystem for Linux.
 Handles incoming mail submission and routing.

Package: nexus-rmc-wsl
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: NexusRMC - WSL Remote Mail Client
 A command-line remote mail client with DKIM/DMARC/SPF support.
 Manages remote mail operations and security checks.
